snippet.title: Ambrosia: Trailer
snippet.description:
Ambrosia is a 2D "Megavania", featuring tight side-scrolling gun-play and exploration. Players customize their weapons with rule-changing mods to build clever contraptions... or just really big guns.

Follow us to stay in touch with development updates!
https://flyambrosia.com
https://twitter.com/realmsoftdevs
https://www.instagram.com/realmsoftdevs/

And have yourself a great day!
